{"tid":1354588,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非] 不如7月27日帶齊祭品去孝敬先人","createTime":"2019-07-23T07:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T07:28:06.000Z","uid":60872,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"90864e7cfa61f3bab1b80a8f028a271a4aa752d9","tid":1354588,"uid":60872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:18:13.000Z","msg":"為咗貫徹和理非精神，建議7月27日元朗遊行以掃墓形式向先人抗議佢地子孫後代所造成嘅慘劇。<br />\n亦希望以祭品孝敬先人，以表達我地只係反對暴力，並非針對鄉紳。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有呢個意向嘅話，希望自發帶齊掃墓所需嘅用品。<br />\n例如：<br />\n1.香燭冥鏹<br />\n2. 祭祀食品 e.g. 燒肉、白切雞、蛋、米酒等<br />\n3. 清除山墳雜草嘅工具<br />\n<br />\n同埋大家都要注意安全，因為燃燒冥鏹容易引起山火，人多嘅時候容易造成受傷。<br />\n<br />\n呢個意見大家點睇？"},{"pid":"a45d2ec53952b004b0db022922900d4ff94804ef","tid":1354588,"uid":60872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:19:36.000Z","msg":"7月27日齊遊行"},{"pid":"61c1adc32f074ebd3767863839c4af6c65b0f32b","tid":1354588,"uid":60872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:20:41.000Z","msg":"7月27日齊遊行"},{"pid":"cfb4148c45e162fa30efbb26a06f8145f711964d","tid":1354588,"uid":60872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:21:01.000Z","msg":"7月27日齊遊行"},{"pid":"2a1975bfdb1c6347abe23179c16025f302350cd0","tid":1354588,"uid":60872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:21:33.000Z","msg":"7月27日齊遊行"},{"pid":"cad64fec7f0ca6deac40aa6e144f779b811e3cd9","tid":1354588,"uid":60872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:23:31.000Z","msg":"7月27日齊遊行"},{"pid":"b1ea8b84d2cea7b8cac729ce019d35658d779e06","tid":1354588,"uid":116166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:28:06.000Z","msg":"唔知佢地鐘唔鐘意飲雞尾酒呢"}]}